{"tid":1462537,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[不割席，但請三思] 主動阻旅客會比政府屈我地脅持人質","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:11:11.000Z","uid":173797,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5515d5dbe7d78f852676484822d92872edf45c","tid":1462537,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"首先，已經發生嘅事唔會割席，但跪求大家諗多一步棋<br />\n<br />\n如果我地主動出手阻旅客，個無賴政府係可以屈我地<span style=\"color: red;\">脅持旅客做人質</span>，甚至誣衊我地係<span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖襲擊</span>！！！<br />\n到時啲狗甚至支共就可以大條道理血洗機場「拯救人質」<br />\n<br />\n明白大家想癱瘓機場做籌碼，但我地只適宜<span style=\"color: blue;\">脅持機場(死物)</span>，而唔可以<span style=\"color: red;\">脅持旅客(人)</span><br />\n今日的確個問題係唔夠琴日咁多人可以迫政府主動跪低<br />\n但唔夠人嘅時候都可以回歸基本步做輸出革命<br />\n唔好忘記琴日去機場嘅初衷係機場唔易被人清場又可以喺國際上make noise，而令到機場停止運作係一個<strong><ins>bonus</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以依家機場係有<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>兩種玩法</strong></span>，夠人就迫政府主動停機，唔夠人就和你飛<br />\n我地應該要喺兩種玩法之間靈活變通，盡量唔好比位人入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"62da7cd74fe2588983cc62077808fa4553ebeb04","tid":1462537,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d117548dd456c78654404b909e1733a5a5ecd65d","tid":1462537,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:49:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd91c6a608ad735a0641333b1694da702e59c06","tid":1462537,"uid":293256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:49:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1d02c0304be8827e73bed007b414433a6f0f0eb","tid":1462537,"uid":66202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"係啲分化撚洗緊版想搞到人唔去機場, 唔好推嗰啲post加入罵戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場要人呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"331a9d3103da6612f93b6297f89540debb087191","tid":1462537,"uid":16458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:50:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b17fd575b60fee1ef01a45ccaa11c732180e573e","tid":1462537,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0d3ddf864006619d671746fa82a532096f80473","tid":1462537,"uid":234550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"冇錯，你阻旅客會令到好多人由支持變反對。<br />\n我唔割蓆，但大家需要反思點做，唔可以俾位林奠翻身"},{"pid":"e7687a38d1354c497b9bcb6e45ea9e78bf9d9ce3","tid":1462537,"uid":173797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要話比全世界知香港沒有暴徒只有暴政<br />\n咁更加唔好比位人地屈我地係恐怖分子"},{"pid":"826fa7d4c9cb0e6666fc7a4f4c73071715945e8d","tid":1462537,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06b00386ea205820e72b3cce38c5a08aa7a91847","tid":1462537,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88b9ae1a19b1c866299dde30f2ea22f5f1bef8c5","tid":1462537,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d984316b0f369e28b37249418bc7da97c2f87439","tid":1462537,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"癱瘓機場係可以重擊政府<br />\n但係明刀明槍阻人上機嗰個唔可以係我地<br />\n千祈唔好成個波讓比政府"}]}